# OpenCode internal state — only design plans in `.omo/plans/` are
# tracked; everything else under `.omo/` (boulder.json, drafts/,
# evidence/, notepads/, run-continuation/) is transient / internal.
# Pattern uses `.omo/*` (not `.omo/`) so that the negation below can
# re-include `.omo/plans/` — git cannot re-include a file whose parent
# directory is itself ignored.
.omo/*
!.omo/plans/
!.omo/plans/**